[B]I wonder if they will improve the trade skills in the near future.  I have studied each of the trade skills and have found that none of them are really worth the trouble.  There is much more money to be made hunting.  I would hate another brewing incident to occur.  No 5th level character should have 400 plat.  Hell, I haven't ever seen 400 plat, but a 10th level bard should be able to make a decent living.  There is a lot of time where I would be lucky to make 3 plat a night tailoring.  I can make easily 5 -10 plat hunting wisps.  I would just hate for this to become a Hack'n'Slash game. Now my ranting and raving is done let me know what you think, or if you know of a patch in the near future.  Thanks.[/B][/QUOTE]

